{"title":"眺望春天","authors":["易殿选"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"眺望春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易殿选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在冬天的边缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眺望春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得春天距我很近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手可触，芳芳的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸润着我并且令我深信不疑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍茫的生命在下一刻瑰丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事实上春天离我很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以至我无法说出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那里到这里的距离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它以一千年前的模样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大平原的尽处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被羊群追赶着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地平线一侧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被沉重的阳光召唤着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而这些只能是我的猜测"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从春天的方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看不出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天将要到来的痕迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧索的原野一片岑寂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方铁青色的山岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛正在被严寒贯穿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而我眺望春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于冻土之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向天与地胶着的地方凝视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为温暖的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天开始在我的想象里蔓延"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙不可言又痛苦难耐"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}